[133.383, "o", "\r\n\r\nHere's the plan вҖ” 8 cards on the board with a clear dependency chain:\r\n\r\n```\r\n1. Project scaffold and Cargo setup\r\n   в””в”Җв–ә 2. Arithmetic expression parser (chumsky)\r\n       в””в”Җв–ә 3. Expression evaluator\r\n           в””в”Җв–ә 4. CLI one-shot mode (Calc)\r\n               в””в”Җв–ә 5. REPL with history (Tape)\r\n                   в”ңв”Җв–ә 6. Syntax highlighting (Highlighting)\r\n                   в”ңв”Җв–ә 7. Vim mode toggle (Editing)\r\n                   в””в”Җв–ә 8. Pretty error messages (Errors)\r\n                        вҶ‘ also depends on card 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Card summary:**\r\n\r\n| # | Card | Files | Key concern |\r\n|---|------|-------|-------------|\r\n| 1 | **Scaffold** | `Cargo.toml`, `src/main.rs`, `.gitignore` | Project init, deps, clap CLI |\r\n| 2 | **Parser** | `src/ast.rs`, `src/parser.rs`, `src/lib.rs` | chumsky grammar, operator precedence, spans |\r\n| 3 | **Evaluator** | `src/eval.rs` | AST walk, f64 result, div-by-zero |\r\n| 4 | **CLI one-shot** | `src/main.rs`, `tests/cli.rs` | Wire parseвҶ’eval"]
[0.000, "o", ", exit codes |\r\n| 5 | **REPL** | `src/repl.rs`, `src/main.rs` | rustyline loop, persistent history |\r\n| 6 | **Highlighting** | `src/highlight.rs`, `src/repl.rs` | Highlighter trait, color scheme |\r\n| 7 | **Vim mode** | `src/main.rs`, `src/repl.rs` | `--vim` flag, EditMode config |\r\n| 8 | **Pretty errors** | `src/errors.rs`, `src/main.rs`, `src/repl.rs` | ariadne reports from chumsky spans |\r\n\r\nCards 6, 7, and 8 are independent of each other and can be implemented in parallel once card 5 is done.\r\n\r\nWant to adjust anything вҖ” add/remove cards, change scope, reorder? When you're happy, exit plan mode and use `/implement-loop` to build it all autonomously, or `/implement` for one card at a time.\r\n"]
