[904.847, "o", "## Summary\r\n\r\nAll 7 kanban cards implemented. Board is clear.\r\n\r\n| # | Card | Mode | Tests Added |\r\n|---|---|---|---|\r\n| 1 | Project scaffold and Cargo setup | Sequential | 14 |\r\n| 2 | Arithmetic expression parser with chumsky | Sequential | 18 |\r\n| 3 | Expression evaluator | Sequential | 13 |\r\n| 4 | CLI one-shot mode | Sequential | 5 |\r\n| 5 | REPL mode with history | Sequential | 6 |\r\n| 6 | Pretty error messages (ariadne) | **Parallel** | 11 |\r\n| 7 | Syntax highlighting in REPL | **Parallel** | 12 |\r\n| 8 | Vim mode toggle | **Parallel** | 2 |\r\n\r\n**Final state:** 79 tests passing, 0 failures, 0 warnings, 0 skipped. Cards 6-8 ran in parallel with no conflicts.\r\n"]
