[303.013, "o", "## Summary\r\n\r\nAll 6 kanban cards implemented and verified.\r\n\r\n### Batch 1 (parallel, 4 agents)\r\n| Card | Status | Tests |\r\n|------|--------|-------|\r\n| **Missing Eq derive** on UnaryOp, BinaryOp, EvalError | Done | 75/75 |\r\n| **Duplicated eval logic** вҖ” removed `Expr::eval()` from ast.rs | Done | 75/75 |\r\n| **Box::leak documentation** вҖ” added KNOWN LEAK comments at 3 sites | Done | 75/75 |\r\n| **Vec\\<char\\> allocation** вҖ” replaced with byte-level iteration in colorize() | Done | 75/75 |\r\n\r\n### Batch 2 (parallel, 2 agents)\r\n| Card | Status | Tests |\r\n|------|--------|-------|\r\n| **Public evaluate() &'static str** вҖ” now accepts `&str`, leak handled internally | Done | 75/75 |\r\n| **Duplicated error-report logic** вҖ” extracted `build_parse_error_report` and `build_eval_error_report` helpers | Done | 75/75 |\r\n\r\n### Final verification\r\n- **79/79 tests pass** (69 unit + 6 CLI + 4 doc-tests)\r\n- No cards skipped or failed\r\n- All cards ran in parallel within their batch\r\n"]
